---
const tools = ['Figma', 'Sketch', 'HTML & CSS', 'Webflow', 'WordPress'];
---

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="container about-grid">
    <div class="about-copy reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">About me</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Design thinking, research & a bit of frontend.
      </h2>
      <p>
        My name is Benjamin Emmanuel and I'm passionate about digital product
        design — an exceptional solution creator using UI design, UX research,
        design thinking and frontend development.
      </p>
      <p>
        My everyday tools are the usual culprits —
        <a class="about-link" href="https://sketch.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sketch</a>,
        <a class="about-link" href="https://figma.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Figma</a>
        and <span class="highlight">HTML &amp; CSS</span> for UI development —
        but I regularly work with low-code tools like
        <a class="about-link" href="https://wordpress.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress</a>
        and
        <a class="about-link" href="https://webflow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Webflow</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        When I'm not staring at my laptop, I'm catching up on football (big fan
        of Real Madrid and Arsenal), playing the drums, or spending good time
        with family. An excellent communicator, a leader, husband, father,
        teacher and friend — hardworking yet fun-loving, and a great asset to
        any team.
      </p>
      <div class="tag-row" style="margin-top: 1.6rem;">
        {tools.map((t) => <span class="tag">{t}</span>)}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-portrait reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 120ms; background: radial-gradient(120% 120% at 50% 0%, rgba(251,146,60,0.25), transparent 60%), linear-gradient(160deg, #1a2740, #0a1120); display:grid; place-items:center; padding: 2rem;">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/benjismemoji.png" alt="Benjamin's memoji" style="width: min(70%, 240px); height:auto; aspect-ratio:auto; border-radius:0; box-shadow:none; border:0;" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
